在函数式编程中，考虑以下代码片段：

```javascript
const curryF = f => a => b => f(a, b);
const add = (x, y) => x + y;
const mul = (x, y) => x * y;
const curryAdd = curryF(add);
const curryMul = curryF(mul);
const applyTwice = f => x => f(f(x));
const arr = [1, 2, 3];
const base = 10;
const transform = x => curryAdd(base)(x);
const transformed = arr.map(transform);
const result = transformed.reduce(curryMul, 1);
```

